item.title: CVE-2020-5635|2024-08-04T08:39:25.507Z -- nec%20corporation -- aterm%20sa3500g
item.description: Aterm SA3500G firmware versions prior to Ver. 3.5.9 allows an attacker on the adjacent network to send a specially crafted request to a specific URL, which may result in an arbitrary command execution.
